lead_paragraph: Raymond Felton tied the score late in regulation and then had eight of his 16 points in overtime as the Dallas Mavericks rallied from 23 points down to beat the Denver Nuggets 122-116 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Mavericks Rally to Beat Nuggets 122-116 in Overtime
